SELECT * FROM PricingStrategies WHERE min_price < 100.00 OR max_price > 200.00;

SELECT FoodPrices.name, MarketAnalysis.price, PricingStrategies.strategy_name FROM FoodPrices JOIN MarketAnalysis ON FoodPrices.id = MarketAnalysis.food_id JOIN PricingStrategies ON MarketAnalysis.price BETWEEN PricingStrategies.min_price AND PricingStrategies.max_price;

SELECT f.food_name, p.price, p.date_added, a.market_location FROM food_prices f JOIN market_analysis a ON f.id = a.food_id JOIN pricing_strategies p ON f.id = p.food_id ORDER BY a.analysis_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT f.food_name, a.price_index, p.pricing_model, p.price_threshold FROM food_prices f JOIN market_analysis a ON f.id = a.food_id JOIN pricing_strategies p ON f.id = p.food_id WHERE p.effective_date <= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY f.food_name ASC LIMIT 5;
